The SHR DISTRO OpenEmbedded layer
This layer depends on:

URI: git://github.com/openembedded/oe-core.git
layers: meta
branch: krogoth
revision: HEAD

URI: git://github.com/openembedded/meta-oe.git
layers: meta-oe, meta-efl, meta-gnome, meta-gpe, meta-systemd
branch: krogoth
revision: HEAD

URI: git://github.com/shr-distribution/meta-smartphone.git
layers: meta-shr, meta-fso
branch: krogoth
revision: HEAD

It is recommended to follow the instruction at 
http://www.shr-project.org/trac/wiki/Building%20SHR

After optional but recommended setup of shr-chroot 
"make setup-shr-chroot"
you just setup shr-core repositories and environment settings with
"make setup-shr-core"

If you want to contribute changes, please follow
http://www.shr-project.org/trac/wiki/Howto%20get%20my%20application%20in%20the%20SHR%20feed
and send patches or pull requests to shr-devel@lists.shr-project.org with prefix [meta-shr-distro].

If you want to discuss this layer join us on #openmoko-cdevel on FreeNode IRC network.

Main layer maintainers: Martin 'JaMa' Jansa <Martin.Jansa@gmail.com>, Klaus 'mrmoku' Kurzmann <mok@fluxnetz.de>
